INFO  2026-06-12 01:02:49,805 [shard 0:main] main - application.cc:736 - redpanda.partition_autobalancing_topic_aware:1	- If `true`, Redpanda prioritizes balancing a topic’s partition replica count evenly across all brokers while it’s balancing the cluster’s overall partition count. Because different topics in a cluster can have vastly different load profiles, this better distributes the workload of the most heavily-used topics evenly across brokers.
