INFO  2026-06-12 01:02:49,805 [shard 0:main] main - application.cc:736 - redpanda.raft_learner_recovery_rate:104857600	- Raft learner recovery rate limit. Throttles the rate of data communicated to nodes (learners) that need to catch up to leaders. This rate limit is placed on a node sending data to a recovering node. Each sending node is limited to this rate. The recovering node accepts data as fast as possible according to the combined limits of all healthy nodes in the cluster. For example, if two nodes are sending data to the recovering node, and `raft_learner_recovery_rate` is 100 MB/sec, then the recovering node will recover at a rate of 200 MB/sec.
